##  Overview

**Growth In Learning And Career Pathways** is a full-stack web application built on the MERN stack that empowers students and professionals to discover curated learning roadmaps and career guidance. The platform integrates **Google Gemini AI** to generate intelligent, personalized answers and career advice based on user queries — making it a smart, interactive career companion.

Users can explore skill-based learning paths, ask career-related questions, track their progress, and receive AI-generated guidance — all in one place.

---

##  Features

- **AI-Powered Career Guidance** — Ask any career or learning question and get intelligent answers from Google Gemini
- **Personalized Learning Pathways** — Browse curated roadmaps by domain (Web Dev, Data Science, AI/ML, etc.)
- **User Authentication** — Secure signup/login with JWT-based auth
- **Progress Tracking** — Save and track your learning milestones
- **Chat Interface** — Conversational UI to interact with Gemini AI
- **MongoDB Backend** — All user data, pathways, and history stored in MongoDB
- **Responsive Design** — Fully mobile-friendly React frontend
- **Search & Filter** — Find pathways by skill, domain, or experience level

