##  API Endpoints

### Auth

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | Register a new user |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login and receive JWT token |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Get logged-in user profile |

### Pathways

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/pathways` | Get all learning pathways |
| GET | `/api/pathways/:id` | Get a single pathway by ID |
| POST | `/api/pathways` | Create a new pathway (admin) |
| PUT | `/api/pathways/:id` | Update a pathway |
| DELETE | `/api/pathways/:id` | Delete a pathway |

### AI (Gemini)

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/ai/ask` | Send a prompt to Gemini and get answer |
| GET | `/api/ai/history` | Get chat history for logged-in user |

